Assuming, The Spark standalone cluster has only 1 worker with total 12 cpu cores, 64 G memory.
The application is submitted with below Spark configurations
--executor-memory = 30G
--conf spark.executor.cores=6
--conf spark.task.cpus=1
--conf spark.sql.partitions=12
And one of the job is divided to different stage as shown in the left.
Question, How Spark schedule the Stages and the Tasks?
